#: ../../reference/api.rst:2 97db66743d8a481d85aa582b61583c80
msgid "API Reference"
msgstr "API 参考"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:5 ca5e1d400f6f42e68014660e5d00e66b
msgid "Python API"
msgstr "Python 接口"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:9 7f65e1a8c1a64f7a9b92f1ef3cf52b75
msgid "Initialize VoxCPM from a local model directory."
msgstr "从本地模型目录初始化 VoxCPM。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:11 9daaaaad02514785863966319f0e4d3c
msgid ""
"The model architecture (``voxcpm`` or ``voxcpm2``) is auto-detected from "
"the ``architecture`` field in ``config.json``."
msgstr ""
"模型架构（``voxcpm`` 或 ``voxcpm2``）会根据 ``config.json`` 中的 ``architecture`` "
"字段自动检测。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst 1daa317f175e4517803dd699e5746ba9
#: 43aa9f0f1fbc4288833ed230df99b5f8 659d2eed2089430db9117e6598386267
#: 99bce332d92c43c198f74cddc8b52338 ed66518e1db94503849106cb7da4938f
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "参数"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:13 7914093e41a440e898ff988cb00c74c5
msgid ""
"Local path to the model directory containing weights, configs, and "
"tokenizer files."
msgstr "包含权重、配置与分词器文件的本地模型目录路径。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:14 6e9795ffa9a243b28ba7a8b5ddfe941c
msgid ""
"ModelScope denoiser model id or local path. Set to ``None`` to skip the "
"denoiser entirely."
msgstr "ModelScope 降噪模型 id 或本地路径。设为 ``None`` 可完全跳过降噪器。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:15 a759c4836b5048939cf0ee931a0b2910
msgid "Whether to initialize the ZipEnhancer denoiser pipeline."
msgstr "是否初始化 ZipEnhancer 降噪流水线。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:16 7e061885bb7541a193d37539554b6c02
msgid ""
"Enable ``torch.compile`` acceleration. Disable for debugging or "
"unsupported platforms. This optimization is primarily useful on CUDA."
msgstr "启用 ``torch.compile`` 加速。若用于调试或处于不受支持的平台，请关闭该选项。此优化主要对 CUDA 场景有意义。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:17 ee680f3ec7964c6c833cec4d93b9b42d
msgid ""
"Runtime device. Use ``None`` or ``\"auto\"`` for automatic fallback "
"(``cuda -> mps -> cpu``), or an explicit value such as ``\"cpu\"``, "
"``\"mps\"``, ``\"cuda\"``, or ``\"cuda:0\"``. Explicit requests raise an "
"error instead of silently falling back."
msgstr ""
"运行时设备。使用 ``None`` 或 ``\"auto\"`` 可启用自动回退（``cuda -> mps -> cpu``），"
"也可以显式指定 ``\"cpu\"``、``\"mps\"``、``\"cuda\"`` 或 ``\"cuda:0\"``。"
"显式指定时若不可用会直接报错，而不是静默回退。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:18 f72ad70c83a749ee8723b8e4557f3715
msgid ""
"LoRA configuration. If ``lora_weights_path`` is provided without this, a "
"default config (``enable_lm=True``, ``enable_dit=True``) is created "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"LoRA 配置。若只提供 ``lora_weights_path`` "
"而未提供此项，将自动创建默认配置（``enable_lm=True``、``enable_dit=True``）。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:19 6a7e0675f3754e7ba5758617cee9e4f1
msgid ""
"Path to pre-trained LoRA weights (``.pth`` file or directory containing "
"``lora_weights.ckpt``)."
msgstr "预训练 LoRA 权重路径（``.pth`` 文件，或包含 ``lora_weights.ckpt`` 的目录）。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:32 e1168aa176ba447c8bb254acc6320c59
msgid ""
"Instantiate ``VoxCPM`` from a Hugging Face Hub snapshot. Downloads model "
"weights automatically on first use."
msgstr "从 Hugging Face Hub 快照实例化 ``VoxCPM``。首次使用时会自动下载模型权重。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:34 5102e1ba95de45ffb9dda3bf295e3daa
msgid ""
"Hugging Face repo id (e.g. ``\"openbmb/VoxCPM2\"``) or local directory "
"path."
msgstr "Hugging Face 仓库 id（例如 ``\"openbmb/VoxCPM2\"``）或本地目录路径。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:35 58c4cc28ce6842bdb8ac5d4b0a0a58f7
msgid "Whether to initialize the denoiser pipeline."
msgstr "是否初始化降噪流水线。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:36 4bb4d180fed14848a401240a87fd3565
msgid "Denoiser model id or local path. Ignored when ``load_denoiser=False``."
msgstr "降噪模型 id 或本地路径。当 ``load_denoiser=False`` 时忽略。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:37 ef1a28ee0e5d45b89843922fdc496971
msgid "Custom cache directory for the snapshot download."
msgstr "快照下载的自定义缓存目录。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:38 3a673e9b750d4473866355eb583ed9c7
msgid "If ``True``, only use local files and do not attempt to download."
msgstr "若为 ``True``，仅使用本地文件，不尝试下载。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:39 6e71f4ffee874136b2b4f9e1cef43ec2
msgid ""
"Enable ``torch.compile`` acceleration. This is primarily a CUDA "
"optimization."
msgstr "启用 ``torch.compile`` 加速。这主要是一项面向 CUDA 的优化。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:40 232132748a5e4cf990bc7a3d8166ab82
msgid ""
"Runtime device. ``None`` / ``\"auto\"`` uses automatic fallback. Explicit"
" choices such as ``\"cpu\"``, ``\"mps\"``, ``\"cuda\"``, and "
"``\"cuda:0\"`` are validated and do not auto-fallback."
msgstr ""
"运行时设备。``None`` / ``\"auto\"`` 会使用自动回退。"
"显式指定 ``\"cpu\"``、``\"mps\"``、``\"cuda\"``、``\"cuda:0\"`` 等值时会进行校验，且不会自动回退。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:41 8183617b120040028fb10c8664df39db
msgid "LoRA configuration for fine-tuned models."
msgstr "微调模型的 LoRA 配置。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:42 b024f0791dd04ee493eb611e39594691
msgid "Path to LoRA weights. If provided, LoRA is loaded after initialization."
msgstr "LoRA 权重路径。若提供，将在初始化后加载 LoRA。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst 04e760a0b65c46b79d6915d205ba0c67
#: 058ed6940c1a4c858a47a76689bf4372 1812c8119edb4865b3807bf9a806e60c
#: 2d6bdc928304456d96b473403fda5c41 ea4cea6c147447f5b765859fa8142aa3
msgid "Returns"
msgstr "返回"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:43 82a8e51a44e749b798eb53e566f5d8d2
msgid "Initialized VoxCPM instance."
msgstr "已初始化的 VoxCPM 实例。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst 08901f8843c84488bd332c49a07255e4
#: 65552001886f46a082134d211bedc05d b148824c9e6044598ab8b713dce97277
#: cbe1fd1be17f44be94e4f86d7931c9b1 ffead2f5c65649029545ca2b0c770b7b
msgid "Return type"
msgstr "返回类型"

#: ../../reference/api.rst 728756469ce24ba3952635c00c234331
#: 91599597cf7d469fa838c31a64f43e74 9e93dbd5ba5c40a38a328d9be4b350d5
msgid "Raises"
msgstr "抛出"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:45 093f0cc03b12438b88edf652368d8ef4
msgid "If ``hf_model_id`` is empty."
msgstr "当 ``hf_model_id`` 为空时。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:58 cb4a85c3fea94017ab5a7349738785b5
msgid "Synthesize speech from text."
msgstr "从文本合成语音。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:60 46194da4dfda448d815526c932f7c0fc
msgid ""
"Input text to synthesize. For Voice Design, prepend control instructions "
"in parentheses: ``\"(warm female voice)Hello\"``."
msgstr "待合成的输入文本。用于 Voice Design 时，在括号中加入控制指令，例如：``\"(warm female voice)Hello\"``。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:61 bad9fca4d6ff446791ae9947995e6204
msgid ""
"Prompt audio path for continuation-style cloning. Must be paired with "
"``prompt_text``. For Hi-Fi cloning, combine it with "
"``reference_wav_path``."
msgstr ""
"延续式克隆的 prompt 音频路径，须与 ``prompt_text`` 配对。Hi-Fi 克隆时可与 "
"``reference_wav_path`` 组合使用。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:62 e7066598a5f44d349477b9a3939db812
msgid ""
"Exact transcript of the prompt audio. Must be provided together with "
"``prompt_wav_path``."
msgstr "prompt 音频的逐字转写，必须与 ``prompt_wav_path`` 同时提供。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:63 9e89dee92b434e548c403c0dbd440149
msgid ""
"Reference audio path for isolated voice cloning (**VoxCPM 2 only**). Can "
"be used alone or combined with ``prompt_wav_path`` + ``prompt_text``."
msgstr ""
"独立音色克隆的参考音频路径（**仅 VoxCPM 2**）。可单独使用，或与 ``prompt_wav_path`` + "
"``prompt_text`` 组合。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:64 ad43615ce5a84c0c8ddee089b6ad7d46
msgid ""
"Guidance scale. Higher values follow the conditioning more strictly; "
"lower values allow more variation. Recommended: 1.0–3.0."
msgstr "引导强度。数值越高越严格遵循条件；越低变化越大。建议 1.0–3.0。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:65 4476b40bfbf94bc0b5fc051e8cbdcc3b
msgid ""
"Number of diffusion steps. More steps improve detail at the cost of "
"speed. Recommended: 4–30."
msgstr "扩散步数。步数越多细节越好、速度越慢。建议 4–30。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:66 560d536fe19042c99f6b82edeb4eca55
msgid "Minimum audio length in model tokens."
msgstr "模型 token 意义上的最短音频长度。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:67 f6de08d1c11444daa42aec41df54286a
msgid "Maximum token length during generation. Increase for very long outputs."
msgstr "生成时的最大 token 长度。输出很长时可增大。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:68 cd13154b07d6453f919f2a3a25766bdb
msgid "Run text normalization (expand numbers, dates, etc.) before generation."
msgstr "生成前进行文本规范化（展开数字、日期等）。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:69 616bd1bfa5954c46b9bcb5da0b65782f
msgid ""
"Denoise prompt/reference audio before generation. Requires the denoiser "
"to be loaded."
msgstr "生成前对 prompt/参考音频降噪。需已加载降噪器。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:70 8b9d4f06f4f54a3e9028fea80ee7d7a8
msgid ""
"Automatically retry when the generated audio length is abnormally short "
"or long."
msgstr "当生成音频时长异常偏短或偏长时自动重试。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:71 68ae3479bd0d43beab7a896cb1783069
msgid "Maximum number of bad-case retries."
msgstr "坏例重试的最大次数。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:72 b0fbe2d3cbee4cd0a26080ddafc50a53
msgid "Audio-to-text duration ratio threshold for bad-case detection."
msgstr "坏例检测用的音频与文本时长比阈值。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:73 121c2db49f4042fbbecee3ea54ac5192
msgid ""
"1-D waveform array (float32). Sample rate is available at "
"``model.tts_model.sample_rate``."
msgstr "一维波形数组（float32）。采样率见 ``model.tts_model.sample_rate``。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:75 11ef4e4028e14348a1a314c2af230c54
msgid "If ``text`` is empty."
msgstr "当 ``text`` 为空时。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:76 b4e6321bcf634d23a353cbcb46bbc652
msgid ""
"If ``prompt_wav_path`` and ``prompt_text`` are not both provided or both "
"``None``."
msgstr "当 ``prompt_wav_path`` 与 ``prompt_text`` 未同时提供或同时为 ``None`` 时。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:77 c2dda2dad6fb4a65bde9885df620ae5d
msgid "If ``reference_wav_path`` is used with a VoxCPM 1.x model."
msgstr "当在 VoxCPM 1.x 模型上使用 ``reference_wav_path`` 时。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:78 eec088c441394bb1b8871ad945901cc8
msgid "If audio file paths do not exist."
msgstr "当音频文件路径不存在时。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:105 50d52dbd46be41908a9924039c3f093e
msgid ""
"Same interface as :py:meth:`generate`, but returns a generator that "
"yields audio chunks incrementally."
msgstr "接口与 :py:meth:`generate` 相同，但返回以增量方式产出音频块的生成器。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:107 7387202ebe73419898df598b893cd30b
msgid "All parameters are identical to :py:meth:`generate`."
msgstr "所有参数与 :py:meth:`generate` 一致。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:109 e39c0d75817448f78cb2558e2be7d3b7
msgid "Generator yielding 1-D waveform chunks (float32)."
msgstr "产出 float32 一维波形块的生成器。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:124 c9d4c7d933654e11aef65d3477bef8cc
msgid "Load LoRA weights from a checkpoint file or directory."
msgstr "从检查点文件或目录加载 LoRA 权重。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:126 e3c00786b7384ace9f42bc056a146611
msgid ""
"Path to LoRA weights (``.pth`` file or directory containing "
"``lora_weights.ckpt``)."
msgstr "LoRA 权重路径（``.pth`` 文件，或包含 ``lora_weights.ckpt`` 的目录）。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:127 ee1a73c251c24b2a9bbc84054d6a6476
msgid ""
"``(loaded_keys, skipped_keys)`` — lists of loaded and skipped parameter "
"names."
msgstr "``(loaded_keys, skipped_keys)`` — 已加载与已跳过参数名的列表。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:129 6cf59811e6774b0b9b444271cae4cf2c
msgid "If model was not initialized with a LoRA config."
msgstr "当模型未以 LoRA 配置初始化时。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:134 128266f99b5a49d4b774f32b4cc0b7d3
msgid ""
"Reset all LoRA weights to their initial state (effectively zeroing them "
"out). The LoRA layers remain in the model but have no effect."
msgstr "将所有 LoRA 权重重置为初始状态（等效清零）。LoRA 层仍保留在模型中但不起作用。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:139 d37bba6d7f3a48399b75c5b69c912bc1
msgid "Enable or disable LoRA layers without unloading weights."
msgstr "在不卸载权重的情况下启用或禁用 LoRA 层。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:141 d92f1a64a1cf42a487ef07f1245f1a06
msgid "``True`` to activate LoRA; ``False`` to use the base model only."
msgstr "``True`` 启用 LoRA；``False`` 仅使用基座模型。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:146 3d427ea7f6274b5b820dfb206d63b392
msgid "Get the current LoRA parameters."
msgstr "获取当前 LoRA 参数。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:148 173d35faffc54a458985bfc11b43fc31
msgid "State dict containing all ``lora_A`` and ``lora_B`` parameters."
msgstr "包含全部 ``lora_A`` 与 ``lora_B`` 参数的状态字典。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:155 8ef5795fd9984dc2b61bd7eb557ca2b0
msgid "``True`` if a LoRA config is currently loaded on this model."
msgstr "若当前模型已加载 LoRA 配置则为 ``True``。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:161 93405b2693cf4e6089999c9e353657c7
msgid "CLI"
msgstr "命令行接口"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:163 5f3c794fb11a4114bfad55b22bb543bc
msgid ""
"The ``voxcpm`` command provides three subcommands. Default model: "
"``openbmb/VoxCPM2``."
msgstr "``voxcpm`` 命令提供三个子命令。默认模型：``openbmb/VoxCPM2``。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:166 0c44cac5963d42d2b4f5f8fa528bf670
msgid "Subcommands"
msgstr "子命令"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:172 5a2068aff8eb47f9b661caa0748803e8
msgid ""
"Generate speech from text without any reference audio. Optionally "
"describe the target voice with ``--control``."
msgstr "无需参考音频，从文本生成语音。可选使用 ``--control`` 描述目标音色。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:183 94a4791be904440ea6de4fa3e1f242a6
msgid "Clone a voice using reference audio or prompt audio with transcript."
msgstr "使用参考音频，或带转写的 prompt 音频进行声音克隆。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:203 7a6b89affc6d41b9bc1574e3e2108f8d
msgid ""
"Process a text file where each line becomes a separate output WAV "
"(``output_001.wav``, ``output_002.wav``, ...)."
msgstr "处理文本文件，每行生成一个独立的输出 WAV（``output_001.wav``、``output_002.wav``、……）。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:211 d5885eb6361f43c1988b0ce0d119f974
msgid "Arguments"
msgstr "参数说明"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:213 5daa96e8e29341fbabe9e294f56309fa
msgid "**Generation**"
msgstr "**生成**"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:217 ea2edd99667b4ba9b6e3c18910169ddf
msgid "Text to synthesize."
msgstr "待合成文本。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:221 4da9f9cbf137479f9401b4f86c0afed1
msgid ""
"Control instruction for voice design or style control (e.g. ``\"warm "
"female voice\"``). Cannot be used together with ``--prompt-text``."
msgstr "音色设计或风格控制的指令（例如 ``\"warm female voice\"``）。不可与 ``--prompt-text`` 同时使用。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:225 53ae7ee5818d43c8a94da54a4d96b9b2
msgid "CFG guidance scale. Default: ``2.0``. Recommended: 1.0–3.0."
msgstr "CFG 引导强度。默认：``2.0``。建议：1.0–3.0。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:229 fd8dd496172245a2b46c20e253813d7f
msgid "Number of diffusion steps. Default: ``10``. Recommended: 4–30."
msgstr "扩散步数。默认：``10``。建议：4–30。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:233 20a42f3ce4cb4f969fc1532a28c47cf9
msgid "Enable text normalization (expand numbers, dates, etc.)."
msgstr "启用文本规范化（展开数字、日期等）。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:235 47b3f46c483d4dadb691eb95246a8e70
msgid "**Prompt & Reference Audio**"
msgstr "**Prompt 与参考音频**"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:239 62c1f81b4ea54705b15e94def557a032
msgid ""
"Prompt audio file for continuation mode. Requires ``--prompt-text`` or "
"``--prompt-file``."
msgstr "延续模式下的 prompt 音频文件。需要 ``--prompt-text`` 或 ``--prompt-file``。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:243 dc4c57a5a9cc4184aaf0156bb6f26756
msgid "Text transcript of the prompt audio."
msgstr "prompt 音频的文本转写。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:247 9b6dae81115f40dc926dccf4e845510e
msgid ""
"Text file containing the prompt transcript (alternative to ``--prompt-"
"text``)."
msgstr "包含 prompt 转写的文本文件（``--prompt-text`` 的替代方式）。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:251 841205acd0014279b6b0a13f12db8a5a
msgid "Reference audio for isolated voice cloning (VoxCPM 2 only)."
msgstr "独立音色克隆的参考音频（仅 VoxCPM 2）。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:255 52c4d6233ebf4ea082ec62a14e39eee6
msgid "Denoise prompt/reference audio with ZipEnhancer before generation."
msgstr "生成前使用 ZipEnhancer 对 prompt/参考音频降噪。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:257 4356d36d07c0403ca74a39db332f190a
msgid "**Model Loading**"
msgstr "**模型加载**"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:261 0821cef1ea09438eb296240f9d0fa55c
msgid "Local model directory. If set, ``--hf-model-id`` is ignored."
msgstr "本地模型目录。若设置则忽略 ``--hf-model-id``。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:265 1909482594ef43a1af14861e5a8dbcf2
msgid "Hugging Face repo id. Default: ``openbmb/VoxCPM2``."
msgstr "Hugging Face 仓库 id。默认：``openbmb/VoxCPM2``。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:269 781d900b36af474e9030c230046a879e
msgid ""
"Runtime device selection. Supported values are ``auto``, ``cpu``, "
"``mps``, ``cuda``, and indexed CUDA devices such as ``cuda:0``. ``auto`` "
"prefers ``cuda -> mps -> cpu``. Explicit values raise an error instead of"
" silently falling back."
msgstr ""
"运行时设备选择。支持 ``auto``、``cpu``、``mps``、``cuda``，以及像 ``cuda:0`` 这样的带索引 CUDA 设备。"
"``auto`` 会优先按 ``cuda -> mps -> cpu`` 选择。显式指定的值若不可用会直接报错，而不是静默回退。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:276 a68aacd033414fbb86c9a97664018a36
msgid "Cache directory for Hub downloads."
msgstr "Hub 下载的缓存目录。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:280 6468d3559b1d4277b123fa17f614aadc
msgid "Only use local files, do not download from Hub."
msgstr "仅使用本地文件，不从 Hub 下载。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:284 49fad07c07e348baadef57e4f209dcb3
msgid "Skip loading the denoiser model."
msgstr "跳过加载降噪模型。"

#: ../../reference/api.rst:288 79f7a793ac4d43919750c2d8cf43bab4
msgid ""
"Disable ``torch.compile`` acceleration. This is commonly useful for "
"debugging, unsupported platforms, and non-CUDA environments."
